From the confd-openroadm directory do the following:

1. Put the confd installation file (e.g. confd-basic-7.2.0.1.linux.x86_64.installer.bin) in this directory.

2. Build docker image:
    docker build -t confd-openroadm .

3. Run docker container with device x (x = roadma, roadmb, roadmc, xpdra or xpdrc)
    run-device.sh x
